{"tid":1814981,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"五毛請入","createTime":"2020-01-07T07:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T07:56:35.000Z","uid":235535,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e36452e5d7367108f70bb2d3fa884451a6b03e63","tid":1814981,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:40:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉鬼 不了<br />\n和勇不分</span></span></strong><br />\n和理非表示 永遠支持勇武 相信前線決定<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記住和勇不分唔係口號 係行動 係承諾</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支持五毛退場<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6c9dac44a94ca70235be7c030b91eaa84f71132","tid":1814981,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:40:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"01bbe5111a58f4e24cd664f2c20e67b44abdc135","tid":1814981,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:41:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d122146f979c3b535d1719b78a91ccf7b27bf2f","tid":1814981,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:41:09.000Z","msg":"【借位宣傳，與主題內容無關】<br />\n<br />\n試下用<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「冇雙普選就獨立 / 沒有普選唯有獨立」</strong></span>做口號<br />\n<br />\n牌面上你係爭取緊無人有異議既雙普選。實質上你提供緊清晰既路徑，解釋緊點解要獨立、以及為獨立提供正當性。<br />\n<br />\n對於和理非，一開始可以則重係「雙普選」上面。但潛移默化地灌輸佢地獨立既可行性。對於獨派，亦解決左「時機」問題；因為嚴格上口號並唔係直接提倡獨立，但同時宣傳緊獨立。"},{"pid":"36e8050f50fb0fa3a9d40d487530d0f15469cb46","tid":1814981,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:41:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LtXpju5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLtXpju5.jpg&h=3136f52d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"262524b8d8d32a7ffd665759d0129616eb4fd213","tid":1814981,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:41:51.000Z","msg":"香港獨立 唯一出路"